name: [Remix me] Contact Card Minisite
description:
Use this file as a starting point. Feel free to detach anything. Add your avatar. Add your name. Change the colors. Change everything. Get creative! Make it yours!

To remix, duplicate this file, make your modifications (make it better, hellooo), and then publish! Be sure to change the cover to a preview of your tasty new design!

 Let’s see what you can make!
